%section.width3.first
  %h4 Add a project
  %p.box Write your concept below. Start with a 30 word description, fill us in on the details, and upload supporting documents. Try to be precise. Finish up with what kind of feedback you might be interested in.

  - form_for(@project,nil, :class => 'column width3 first') do |f|
    != render :partial => 'form', :locals => { :f  => f }
    %p.actions.width3.first
      != f.submit 'Create'
      or
      != link_to 'Cancel', projects_path
